lead_paragraph: Volkswagen is set to pull out of the world rally championship at the end of the season, with the decision coming only days after the German manufacturer won a fourth successive title, specialist media reported on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Volkswagen to Pull Out of World Championship-Reports
